<h1 id="about-big-bad-wolf">About Big Bad Wolf</h1>
<p>Join the Big Bad Wolf as he tries to catch the three little pigs. Big Bad Wolf is a slot with the standard five reels and three lines taking place in the world of the three little pigs and the Big Bad Wolf. This is the first game in the Quickspin portfolio running the “Swooping Reels” feature. because of the Swooping Reels, Pigs Turn Wild combination a game round can go on, and on, and on…</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>First of the features in Big Bad Wolf we have the Swooping Reels feature. Working much like the Avalanche or Cascade functions from NetEnt and Play N’ Go Swooping Reels removes any winning symbols replacing them with new ones that swoop down from above. Wins will always be triggering re-spins in games with this feature.<br>
This game also has free spins activating the Blowing Down the House feature.</p>
<h3 id="pigs-turn-wild-feature">Pigs Turn Wild Feature</h3>
<p>Since this slot uses Swooping Reels not rewarding consecutive wins wasn’t an option. Because of this we’re presenting the Pigs Tun Wild feature. A feature where every second swoop is turning one of the Pig symbols into a wild. Reaching the maximum of three wild pigs requires six consecutive wins.</p>
<h3 id="blowing-down-the-house-feature">Blowing Down the House Feature</h3>
<p>Accessing the Blowing Down the House feature requires three Scatter symbols showing up on the board. When this happens ten free spin activates. In the free spin rounds you’re collecting Moon symbols on the last reel. Every Moon symbol causes you to huff and puff and blow down a house. Blowing down a house gives you a multiplier.</p>
